name: Mimosa Vermillion | Black Clover
description:
Lora of Mimosa Vermillion from Black Clover

For your outfit use in v2:

mage_dress, golden_cape,mimosa_earrings, white sleeves, white skirt

With a weight between 0.7 and 0.8.

--For the rest of the suit, a weight of 0.6 was used.

For your outfit use in v1:

mage_dress, golden_cape, white skirt, red earrings, capelet, fur trim, red cape, brown boots, white sleeves, belt

With a weight between 0.7 and 0.8.

--For the rest of the suit, a weight of 0.6 was used.

Clarifications

Recommended weight between 0.5 and 0.8.

For all the photos the model yesmix v15 was used

You can download the photos to see the complete specifications

modelVersions.name: v2
modelVersions.description: There are no longer as many illustrations with shadows on the face as before, and some trigger words have been changed. Although with mage_dress and golden_cape the suit already comes out well on several occasions, it is also recommended to add white sleeves, white skirt
